JayBizzle: That would depend on what you are using to view and listen to this avi file and on what system. Like myself for instance, I am on a Power Mac G5 running Leopard. I find that in some programs like Quicktime I can not hear or see when I run the file but if I use another program like VLC my problem is solved. To get the same file to run in quicktime, I would have to download a third-party plugin like divx and niceplayer. HTH
